Distribution notes
------------------

- This repository contains the application shell and tooling, not the original wiki snapshot itself.
- Public releases should clearly attribute the source wiki and should not describe the content pack as an official mirror.
- If the content licensing status becomes unclear or incompatible with redistribution, stop shipping the content pack and keep the app available as an importer/reader shell only.
